{"tid":1074843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人宣過誓？","createTime":"2019-03-23T16:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T03:58:32.000Z","uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ce7ff5cac6fab37ca621953511ebee3a7c870c","tid":1074843,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:32:18.000Z","msg":"我老豆出世嗰時屋企行船，阿嫲喺船上生咗佢，宜家政府話因為我阿爺同阿嫲都過咗身，唔肯俾出世紙佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係宜家美國問緊佢拎出世證明，所以宜家要宣誓，想問一問咁樣寫得唔得？<br />\n<br />\n我（xxx）, 在這宣明我在xxxx年xx月xx日出生於香港。<br />\n因為我的雙親已經過世，所以我不能申請我的出生證明書。<br />\n在此申明我是在香港出生，及也是一個香港永久居民。<br />\n<br />\n老豆寫嘅，我之後再譯翻英文俾美國，佢應該要將中文版交多一次俾政府<br />\n<br />\nPS: 移民用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f89d300bac5230d64cdfa084ddc52116219d7c","tid":1074843,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宣誓唔是揾律師就識搞？"},{"pid":"09eb7766bb3076ae467b3b434b6199e7b5b335d6","tid":1074843,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17f89d300bac5230d64cdfa084ddc52116219d7c","tid":1074843,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宣誓唔是揾律師就識搞？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"政府叫佢去民政處宣誓，喺香港唔駛律師，喺美國先要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680792c173ab4c9d6fe0dd18b424cd3d856b6d43","tid":1074843,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵律師問下<br />\n<br />\n唔知美國要求係點....."},{"pid":"092b7c953ac56cce6a35309bffd165e8c807f6d6","tid":1074843,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"屌你行字係都用英文寫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e0f39a520e8929889b5e166